WEBVTT

00:07:29.506 --> 00:07:32.262
So they took out loans and planted.

00:07:32.262 --> 00:07:33.752
For the next three weeks,

00:07:33.752 --> 00:07:36.060
there wasn't a single drop of rain,

00:07:36.060 --> 00:07:38.624
and the crops that had germinated so well

00:07:38.624 --> 00:07:41.937
shriveled and died.

00:07:41.937 --> 00:07:44.692
We'd insured the loans of a microfinance institution

00:07:44.692 --> 00:07:45.812
that had provided those loans

00:07:45.812 --> 00:07:49.360
to about 6,000 farmers in that area,

00:07:49.360 --> 00:07:50.650
and we called them up and said,

00:07:50.650 --> 00:07:52.350
"Look, we know about the drought.

00:07:52.350 --> 00:07:54.014
We've got you.

00:07:54.014 --> 00:07:58.327
We'll give you 200,000 Euros
at the end of the season."

00:07:58.327 --> 00:08:00.126
They said, "Wow, that's great,